The Extraordinary African Chambers (French: Chambres Africaines Extraordinaires, CAE) bụ ụlọ ikpe e guzobere n'okpuru nkwekọrịta dị n'etiti African Union na Senegal iji kpee ikpe mpụ mba ụwa mere na Chad site na 7 June 1982 ruo 1 Disemba 1990

Oge a dabara na ọchịchị onye isi ala Chad bụ Hissène Habré. E meghere Ụlọ Nzukọ Africa pụrụ iche na 8 Febụwarị 2013 na Dakar, Senegal.Onye ọka ikpe Ciré Aly Bâ bụ onye nchịkwa ugbu a nke ụlọ ọgbakọ pụrụ iche nke Africa na ụlọikpe Senegal.
